{"tid":1794810,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「叫春」告一段落...","createTime":"2019-12-23T11:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T16:13:21.000Z","uid":213538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d00b373f5ae8b1b5a8613982ffca39c7201ff48","tid":1794810,"uid":213538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"雖然我好唔捨得你，<br />\n但係都已經block左我，<br />\n我唔死心都唔得<br />\n我唔知你對我仲有無感覺<br />\n但係我話你知我真係當你係我屋企人咁<br />\n你會覺得我好撚廢或者唔夠細心/善忘<br />\n連呢啲咁重要既野我都可以過一排就無左回事<br />\n我應該對你著緊啲，多啲陪你<br />\n但係我無做到，將個注意力放左係第二到<br />\n係我有負於你<br />\n你係第二個post到留言我係睇到<br />\n但係你唔洗再改名/block我了<br />\n我唔會再煩住你，我會用呢條刺緊記今日既教訓<br />\n希望我可以快啲走出呢個谷底<br />\n或者將來我地會係街上撞到，<br />\n我希望可以好好打聲招呼，了解大家既近況<br />\n最後，我想同你講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥豬怡，對唔住<br />\n我唔係希望你原諒我，我只係想個心過得舒服啲"},{"pid":"5f2e74c0603db397ebcc5e30fca407b22ce8591b","tid":1794810,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"陳怡？"},{"pid":"5d352200f646d60966667274534b58d00312e50a","tid":1794810,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肥豬怡</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78766938ccce85ed0939868266c1ca0955dbb98b","tid":1794810,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"肥豬怡見倒肯撚定得淡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}